{"tid":2487124,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"叙福樓黃傑龍：寧少做生意 不迫員工顧客打針嘟碼","createTime":"2021-04-13T10:34:53.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-29T06:51:34.000Z","uid":39464,"like":78,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"36cf7b5b96f18ba9805cdd6d4ec8ce442f30ec5e","tid":2487124,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T10:34:53.000Z","msg":"黃傑龍受訪時指，雖然支持政府防疫，但不認同以強迫手段達到目的。雖然員工打針換來放寬食肆營業限制很吸引，但只對老闆有利，員工可謂「零誘因」，更可能衍生不必要的勞資糾紛，「如果老闆為咗開多2個鐘，迫員工打針，咁會唔會係剝削勞工權益？爭取咗幾十年，而家一下子倒退哂。」<br />\n<br />\n除了打針，黃傑龍也指，未來也不會強迫顧客必須使用「安心出行」程式，來換取放寬營業限制，「迫人用『安心出行』係冇用，亦唔見得一定好過填紙仔，紙仔起碼有（顧客的）電話號碼，有個機會搵到佢；而家大把人拎個平時唔會用嘅電話去嘟『安心出行』，你所謂通知佢都冇用，佢唔開部手機嚟睇，我唔覺得係有用咗」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210413/6F46ZAMZZFHQVMKKXGTASLVT5I/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210413%2F6F46ZAMZZFHQVMKKXGTASLVT5I%2F&d=anIIoOx73pQIzJB4hJH11Im5R6Uo%2BMV3ZOx7awwfaZg%3D&h=231522be\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210413%2F6F46ZAMZZFHQVMKKXGTASLVT5I%2F&h=fd37f3b3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210413/6F46ZAMZZFHQVMKKXGTASLVT5I/</a>"},{"pid":"d034aec512ea427c4b4c641d5fcf19a187e61f19","tid":2487124,"uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T10:35:56.000Z","msg":"老細好好人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f38ce01b3283ed2fa9d28d955653a663a9702ab4","tid":2487124,"uid":59283,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T10:35:56.000Z","msg":"黃傑龍好黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c83b50ed3dccc74087f8f4a2795f7ee6c3d24836","tid":2487124,"uid":277659,"like":51,"dislike":0,"score":51,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T10:39:46.000Z","msg":"出面成日話佢扮黃<br />\n扮黃扮到咁<br />\n咪由佢繼續扮"},{"pid":"2909b7fe3f32013eda4bf255bdb65f1118c2e5cb","tid":24